parameters:
\SE[92]I see... So Nikita got separated, huh? \SE[93]I
thought we could be together...

\SE[38]Yeah... When we were camping, we encountered a
beast... It was to let us escape... I hope everyone is
safe...

\SM[nod]\SE[91]I'm sure they're safe. \SE[14]Don't worry.
I'll try looking for them too.

\SE[52]Yeah, that's right... \!\SE\SE[1]But you know, I can
somehow understand what you want to say. \!\SE[1]Earlier,
you were asking Are you staying overnight today?

\SE[21]That was... Vega-san is so cool, it makes my heart
race.
\SE[82]Don't say things that make it hard for me to react...

\SE[84] (Although there have been many difficult things...
\SE[21] I'm glad that both of you are facing them
positively.)

\SE[5]By the way, what are Melissa and the others going to
do from now on? \SE[3]In Yuriseen, Tita and the others are
also there, but...

\SE[2]Um... well, you see. \SE[3]Ronoa is saying that she
wants to stay here a little longer.

\SE[48]Mayor... Actually, recently, I lost my child...
\.Because you seemed lonely, I wanted to be with you.
\!\SE[3]I can't leave Ronoa alone either...

\SE[2]Ah, I see... \SE[90]Well then, I guess there's no
helping it... Yeah.

Melissa... I'm sorry, but can I ask you to gather more
Merukuru Grass? My back has been particularly painful
today...

\SE\SE[0]This is a medicinal herb that can be found around
here. It's said to be effective for shoulder stiffness and
lower back pain. \SE[0]Sometimes I go and gather it.

\SE\SE[0]Then, should we help too? The air is also nice, and
I want to take a little walk... \SE[0]Is it okay? Vega.

\SE[72]Yes, my role is already over. \SE[7]Escort duty
wouldn't be so bad, I suppose.

Well, well... Even the messengers from Yuriseen... I can't
say I'm a replacement, but I'll arrange accommodations, so
it would be good for you to stay there tonight.

Actually, I wanted to let them stay here... That way, these
children would be happy too, but unfortunately, there are no
more beds available...

\SE\SE[21]No, thank you very much. \!\SE[21]I will
gratefully accept your kind offer.

\SE[0]Alright, shall we both go then? \!\SE[2]Where does the
Merukuru Grass grow?

\SE\SE[2]You crossed the bridge before coming to the
village, right? \!\SE[2]Cross over there and...

\SE\SE[0]On the way, there is a lake. \!\SE[0]There, you can
find Merukuru Grass.

\SE[0]If we go nearby, I'll guide you, so I don't think
you'll get lost. Please rest assured.
\SE\SE[0]I see. \SE[0]Well then, shall we depart right away?
\SE (I wonder what she wants to convey.)

\SE Ronoa, you know. She said, I'm glad to see you after a
long time.

\SE Lunaroa seems to have taken a liking to this village...
The village chief is also kind.

\SE I might understand Lunaroa's feelings a little. Maybe
it's because this village reminds me a bit of Hatayaki
Village.
